org.cougaar.core.persist
Interface Persistence

All Known Implementing Classes:
BlackboardPersistence
public interface Persistence

An extended persistence interface for BlackboardPersistence.

The BlackboardPersistence implementation recasts these methods into the new PersistenceService interface.
